8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][vc_row_inner column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; top_padding=&#8221;3%&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221; row_position=&#8221;default&#8221; row_position_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; row_position_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; overflow=&#8221;visible&#8221; pointer_events=&#8221;all&#8221;][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/1&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; animation_type=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][vc_column_text]\n<h2><strong>Anzscosearch &amp; DAMA lists<\/strong><\/h2>\n[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Anzscosearch offers <strong>three different methods<\/strong> to navigate occupations and information under the various <a href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/dama\/\">Designated Area Migration Agreements (DAMAs)<\/a>.[\/vc_column_text][nectar_badge display_tag=&#8221;h5&#8243; bg_color_type=&#8221;global&#8221; color=&#8221;accent-color&#8221; padding=&#8221;small&#8221; border_radius=&#8221;3px&#8221; display=&#8221;block&#8221; text=&#8221;1. Using the Main Searching Tool&#8221;][vc_column_text]In the search box, type an ANZSCO code or name; if the occupation is included in any DAMA lists, a red tag will indicate this with the words \u201cDAMA\u201d. Further information regarding specific lists and concessions is available in the DAMA tab (tractor icon).<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/search\/\">https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/search\/<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][image_with_animation image_url=&#8221;110021&#8243; image_size=&#8221;medium_large&#8221; animation_type=&#8221;entrance&#8221; animation=&#8221;Fade In&#8221; hover_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; border_radius=&#8221;3px&#8221; box_shadow=&#8221;small_depth&#8221; image_loading=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;100%&#8221; max_width_mobile=&#8221;default&#8221; margin_top=&#8221;40&#8243; margin_bottom=&#8221;20&#8243;][nectar_badge display_tag=&#8221;h5&#8243; bg_color_type=&#8221;global&#8221; color=&#8221;accent-color&#8221; padding=&#8221;small&#8221; border_radius=&#8221;3px&#8221; display=&#8221;block&#8221; text=&#8221;2. By accessing each DAMA list independently&#8221;][vc_column_text]Access all active Designated Area Migration Agreement (DAMA) lists independently and obtain Occupation-based information on eligibility and relevant concessions, all on one page. Navigate from one DAMA to another using the appropriate button.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/dama-all\/\">https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/dama-all\/<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][image_with_animation image_url=&#8221;110022&#8243; image_size=&#8221;large&#8221; animation_type=&#8221;entrance&#8221; animation=&#8221;Fade In&#8221; hover_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; constrain_group_1=&#8221;yes&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; border_radius=&#8221;3px&#8221; box_shadow=&#8221;small_depth&#8221; image_loading=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;100%&#8221; max_width_mobile=&#8221;default&#8221; margin_top=&#8221;20&#8243; margin_bottom=&#8221;20&#8243;][nectar_badge display_tag=&#8221;h5&#8243; bg_color_type=&#8221;global&